{"content": "<h2>Tokenised Art for the People</h2>\t\t\n\t\t<p>The first art show at The Line is now open to the public. Launched by owner and founder of The Line, the artist known as MintFace. The music booms from the pavement, nudging those who would otherwise never step inside an art space... to feel the magnetic pull inside.</p>\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img width=\"2560\" height=\"1440\" src=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/gallery-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/gallery-scaled.jpg 2560w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/gallery-300x169.jpg 300w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/gallery-1024x576.jpg 1024w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/gallery-768x432.jpg 768w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/gallery-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/gallery-2048x1152.jpg 2048w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/gallery-800x450.jpg 800w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/gallery-1320x743.jpg 1320w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/gallery-600x338.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\" />\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t<p>The digital tokens and blockchain provenance takes a backstage to the presentation of 25 paintings in the <a href=\"https://twoburdens.com\">Two Burdens collection</a> by MintFace. The art invites the viewer to come to their own conclusions as to what they are seeing, and the art title may be the unlock... or continue to hold the viewer at some distance. Either way, your preconceptions will be tested and expanded.</p>\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figure>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img width=\"2424\" height=\"1256\" src=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/The-Line-gallery-Two-Burdens-collection-MintFace-Hawkes-Bay.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/The-Line-gallery-Two-Burdens-collection-MintFace-Hawkes-Bay.png 2424w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/The-Line-gallery-Two-Burdens-collection-MintFace-Hawkes-Bay-300x155.png 300w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/The-Line-gallery-Two-Burdens-collection-MintFace-Hawkes-Bay-1024x531.png 1024w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/The-Line-gallery-Two-Burdens-collection-MintFace-Hawkes-Bay-768x398.png 768w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/The-Line-gallery-Two-Burdens-collection-MintFace-Hawkes-Bay-1536x796.png 1536w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/The-Line-gallery-Two-Burdens-collection-MintFace-Hawkes-Bay-2048x1061.png 2048w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/The-Line-gallery-Two-Burdens-collection-MintFace-Hawkes-Bay-1320x684.png 1320w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/The-Line-gallery-Two-Burdens-collection-MintFace-Hawkes-Bay-600x311.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2424px) 100vw, 2424px\" />\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figcaption>Gen-O           |     Nuclear Shadows | Through The Forest</figcaption>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</figure>\n\t\t\t<h2>Geodetic Cultural Object</h2>\t\t\n\t\t<p>In the centre of The Line is a tall cultural object with 2021 blockchain provenance, built to scale in real life (IRL). The title of the work is <a href=\"https://geodeti.ca/\">'Geodetica'</a> and is a beacon representative of an almost 10 year long journey of pulsing a signal of location for the disappeared to pick up on. In the meantime, visitors are invited to leave their mark on the Geodetic... reflecting a patina of who has bared witness to its beacon.</p>\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figure>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img width=\"1440\" height=\"2560\" src=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/IMG_6373-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/IMG_6373-scaled.jpg 1440w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/IMG_6373-169x300.jpg 169w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/IMG_6373-576x1024.jpg 576w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/IMG_6373-768x1365.jpg 768w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/IMG_6373-864x1536.jpg 864w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/IMG_6373-1152x2048.jpg 1152w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/IMG_6373-1320x2346.jpg 1320w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/IMG_6373-600x1066.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1440px) 100vw, 1440px\" />\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figcaption>Geodetic Cultural Object</figcaption>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</figure>\n\t\t\t<h2>Private Invitation</h2>\t\t\n\t\t<p>We have events planned...and you'll need an invite. During the day... after work.. and on the livestream. We're curating a list of those who care about what's next at the confluence of art, digital and finance. </p>\t\t\n\t\t\t<iframe loading=\"lazy\"\n\t\t\t\t\tsrc=\"https://maps.google.com/maps?q=318%20Heretaunga%20Street%20West%2C%20Hastings%2C%20&#038;t=m&#038;z=17&#038;output=embed&#038;iwloc=near\"\n\t\t\t\t\ttitle=\"318 Heretaunga Street West, Hastings, \"\n\t\t\t\t\taria-label=\"318 Heretaunga Street West, Hastings, \"\n\t\t\t></iframe>"}